title: Tom Asta: Welcome to Santa Cruz Skateboards!
description: Santa Cruz Skateboards recently acquired Tom Asta to the Pro Lineup, and here's two minutes of ripping Asta footage to celebrate. From Street League, to filming heavy video parts, Asta can't be stopped. Welcome to the squad, Tom! Look out for Tom's part in LRG's 1947 vid coming soon!... Tom Also rides for Ricta Wheels, and MOB Grip.
